 />\n又出名。 又高教學質素<br />\n學生又係尖子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />j 死人咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7431e18212cf79c7de1a9fc2da62fa6327c901cb","tid":197801,"uid":75457,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"客觀黎講<br />\ncu nursing &gt; polyu nursing &gt; hku nursing &gt;ou nursing/護校 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;東華nursing"},{"pid":"c3096d6b744f122ec7321f1b47ed16e084b4dacc","tid":197801,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>客觀黎講<br />\ncu nursing &gt; polyu nursing &gt; hku nursing &gt;ou nursing/護校 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;東華nursing</blockquote><br />\n護校排第一啦下話 點會中大第一"},{"pid":"4b3fb7cc5a945a0b05ac223e5bc5621b467998d3","tid":197801,"uid":16617,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T21:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>客觀黎講<br />\ncu nursing &gt; polyu nursing &gt; hku nursing &gt;ou nursing/護校 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;東華nursing</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCu &gt; Poly？<br />\nHku &gt; Ou？<br />\nOu = 護校？<br />\n從以上已經證明左你幾撚無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀得呢科都唔會唔識排"},{"pid":"1b3a1b7fb4512c8e51ee8c62f6455d8c02068bee","tid":197801,"uid":106030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T21:45:04.000Z","msg":"鳩吹少陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9bb67938fa28f9f017c055f8ec61fc5f753c9d","tid":197801,"uid":6688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T17:42:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ef36f10c4890a28c95840c05837b4a7aed3b457","tid":197801,"uid":81587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:52:01.000Z","msg":"好認真咁樣答你, OU nursing 係好過HKU nursing <br />\nHku 既課程一般比其他院校教得慢，啲學生可以入lab實習既時間都遲d<br />\n利申有2個親戚都係做護士長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主要其實就係OU nursing 你讀5年，每一年都要出實習，咁當然year 1就大多係visit，無咁辛苦。而nursing 呢科好講求實習，啲學生接觸多d，攞多d經驗。<br />\n所以OU都係有優勝之處。<br />\n至於老師方面，OU啲老師絕對唔差，全部都係好有經驗既RN教你skills ，好老實講，nursing skills 呢家野好講經驗，俾你讀多幾個master 都唔會夠你係ward 十年既經驗黎得豐富同教得好<br />\n<br />\n好多人踩ou nursing 易入等等，其實易入又如何？nursing好多既test Exam, practicum 全部都係under HA既guidelines ，一份卷都double check sure 你係堅pass 唔係符碌。你有幾廢/幾勁都好，入到去讀唔掂就係唔掂，一樣要resit一樣無ward出，讀到第8年你都grad唔到一樣係無牌無rn做<br />\n<br />\n講左咁多希望幫到樓主啦 <br />\nbtw nursing 睇bio 多過chem,bio 5都有用過chem 5**事關你入到就要讀解剖學，加油。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69412dd8d6244dea1a821c4e8a54fc1af1f2def","tid":197801,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心ou nursing係好過hku</blockquote><br />\nagree"},{"pid":"18ddbf8577d0190c30185232e8f8f94ff065e79b","tid":197801,"uid":61271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:13:21.000Z","msg":"hku nursing 出名最差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實出到黎做唔做到野，騎唔騎呢，都係睇番果個人<br />\n邊間學校出黎都無乜關係"},{"pid":"c61009ebef4ea49ee2376cbe1d65488c15519843","tid":197801,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T23:00:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"303f500a3cd052e9889d1fa181472460abad9db3","tid":197801,"uid":127363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:00:43.000Z","msg":"學生質素同成績 HKU&gt;OU"},{"pid":"9cc4e338e4fa7fd45bb444c1842abc521f881125","tid":197801,"uid":197610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c69412dd8d6244dea1a821c4e8a54fc1af1f2def","tid":197801,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心ou nursing係好過hku</blockquote><br />\nagree"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"當年我揀科都有好多人話poly practical啲， hku又theoretical 啲咁。最後因爲啲科嘅weighting都係揀hku覺得穩陣啲。<br />\n<br />\n入咗去其實又唔覺得佢唔好喎。開頭係辛苦嘅，life science嗰啲真心唔淺，諗住hea就真係難少少。但過咗嗰啲，其實school都多support。年年出ward前都有啲activities安排嚟温吓skills同書。過咗鴨仔團日子出去出specialty，都有學校老師嚟睇。嗰啲日子其實都幾stressful, 有老師嚟睇我，可以呻吓講吓問吓，簡直係甘露。<br />\n<br />\nGrad咗我又唔覺得hku嗰啲差過人喎，pick up到，仲最早做night IC添。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知其他院校係咪最好，我又無讀過。用家就淨係敢話hku nursing 其實幾好。"},{"pid":"a21c5f7e4684473048449ac608fd176a148b6c24","tid":197801,"uid":139158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"冇話邊間好，邊間唔好。最重要睇你個人。你係醒目讀咩都掂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你可以睇下想過邊種u life"}]}